com.viaoa.util

Class OACircularQueue<TYPE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.util.OACircularQueue<TYPE>

  • public abstract class OACircularQueue<TYPE>
extends java.lang.Object
    Thread safe Circular Queue. There is a single headPostion, and each consumer can have a tailPosition. Client access (getMessageXxx methods) will check overruns, and will throw an exception if a queue overrun occurs. A session id can be used so that entries can be removed from the queue once all sessions have received it.
    Author:
    vvia Note: this is made abstract to be able to get the Generic class that is used.
